dules and runs GIMPLE verification after each pass that requests `TODO_verify_il`. This is the mechanism by which verification is woven into the pass pipeline defined in passes.def.\n\nThe error call chain is: pass sets TODO_verify_il → passes.cc:execute_todo → tree-cfg.cc:verify_gimple_in_seq or verify_gimple_in_cfg → tree-cfg.cc:verify_gimple_in_seq_2 → tree-cfg.cc:verify_gimple_stmt → (on failure) diagnostic-global-context.cc:internal_error(\"%<verify_gimple%> failed\")."
